      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FANCY CHICK (4) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and two placings from 11 starts. Missed the frame latest (20.18) when fifth over 340m at this track in a Mix 1/2/3. Appeals as a leading chance in this. BLUE SUPREME (2) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fifth (20.27) at this track. Solid record at the distance winning nine races. The form out of her last race has been franked. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. DON'T BLUSH BABY (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (20.21) in a Mix 2/3 at this track. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Can figure in the finish. HAYMAN BEACH (1) can return to form after missing the top-three at this circuit last time out.",
